    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable companion that\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so it runs like a dream. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner very happy. Come take it for a spin!",
