    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi everyone! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It runs like a dream and has plenty of life left for all your road trips and daily commutes! It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so you can just hop in and go. If you're looking for something reliable that still looks fantastic on the road, this is the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
