    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound example of this driver-focused platform. This unit features the high-revving naturally aspirated powerplant mated to a precise short-throw 6-speed manual transmission. Key performance enhancements include a factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential (LSD) for superior cornering exit and a track-tuned suspension utilizing Bilstein monotube dampers. The braking system remains robust with four-piston Brembo calipers up front, ensuring fade-resistant deceleration. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the chassis rigidity remains uncompromised and the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and linear power delivery. All fluid services are current, and the cooling system has been overhauled for thermal efficiency.",
